         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">1st May 1857 ¶ Sir, ¶  ¶ I have the honor to acknowledge the receipt of your letter of the 18th Ultimo, ¶  and to inform you that your request therein for an extension of your leave of absence to the ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">57.05.01a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Thomas Balmain</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 57/1202, unit 3, p. 14, VPRS 975/P1 outward registered correspondence, VA 669 Public Works Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">1st May 1857</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to acknowledge the receipt of your letter of the 18th Ultimo,<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">M to C. Duffy, 18 April 1857.</p>
               </note> and to inform you that your request therein for an extension of your leave of absence to the end of June next, has been granted.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">(Signed) T. C. Balmain</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">F. Mueller Esqr</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Botanic Gdns Sydney N.S.W.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3346in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3346in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">See also M to D. Moore, 6 May 1857.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </div>
